name: wpa_supplicant
desc:
WPA Supplicant is a Wi-Fi Protected Access (WPA) client and IEEE 
802.1X supplicant. It implements WPA key negotiation with a WPA 
Authenticator and Extensible Authentication Protocol (EAP) 
authentication with an Authentication Server. In addition, it controls 
the roaming and IEEE 802.11 authentication/association of the wireless 
LAN driver. This is useful for connecting to a password protected 
wireless access point.
